## Environment Setup

### Backend
```bash
cd backend
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # Windows: venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
cp .env.example .env  # Edit with your API keys
python3 server.py
```

### Frontend
```bash
cd frontend
npm install
cp .env.example .env  # Edit with VITE_API_URL
npm run dev
```

